"""
Edwin Fireflies Connector — Meeting transcripts, audio & video

Modes:
  sync <source>   — incremental extraction to data/fireflies/
  status          — show last sync times

Sources: transcripts, audio, video, all
  "all" syncs transcripts only (audio/video are on-demand)

API:
  GraphQL: https://api.fireflies.ai/graphql
  Auth:    Authorization: Bearer <FIREFLIES_API_KEY>
  Rate:    60 requests/minute (Business plan)
"""

